represents the nations largest airlines said a record 7 million 
americans traveled by air during the thanksgiving holiday weekend 
between dec 17 and jan 2 us airlines expect to transport at 
least 22 million people or about 500000 more than for the same 
period last year he said that would also be a record horn said 
the nations major airlines announced last month that they were 
boosting most of their lowest discount fares and eliminating the 
cheap fares that can be booked a few days before a flight but a 
week later eastern continental delta and northwest airlines 
announced reductions in some of their fares 
